snippet.title: Rival Pirates | Official Game Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
Make 'em walk the plank! Set sail, fire cannon balls and be the last boat standing among your enemies in this swashbuckling adventure.

Play Rival Pirates, on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/game/81519741
